<h1>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h1>

<p>The following pantry items are about to expire:</p>

<ul>
  <% @items.each do |item| %>
    <li>
      <strong><%= item.name %></strong> — expires on <%= item.expiry_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Please take necessary action before they expire.</p>

<p>— Pocket Pantry Team</p>
